$NetBSD$

${PKGNAME} has been installed in ${PREFIX}/${MCALCBASE}
To access ${PKGNAME} point your favorite JavaScript capable web
broswer to ${PREFIX}/${MCALCBASE}/index.html

To make this available via a running httpd server, you must either
map the directory ${PREFIX}/${MCALCBASE} or copy the contents
of that directory to one used by your httpd server.
